definitions.definition: A bird hunted or kept for food, grouped into landfowl (order Galliformes ), also called gamefowl , and waterfowl (order Anseriformes : ducks , geese , swans , etc.), which together form the clade Galloanserae .

main_definition: A bird hunted or kept for food, grouped into landfowl (order Galliformes ), also called gamefowl , and waterfowl (order Anseriformes : ducks , geese , swans , etc.), which together form the clade Galloanserae .
